choice_30:
Imagine that, as a gift, you're going to cook dinner for a friend who is currently on crutches and can't cook for themselves. You have $20 to buy the ingredients, and forty-five minutes (after shopping) to prepare the meal. You know that your friend is allergic to anything with seeds, prefers foods that don't require too much chewing, and dislikes foods that are moist. What would you cook them?
(After thirty seconds, you'll be able to advance the page.)
